1.1.name: wordpress/victorian-xmas
1.1.description: A WordPress 3 theme for Christmas. Customised attachment and image templates are included. Sticky post highlighting, post thumbnail support and threaded comments. Folding page and category menus. Support available at http://forum.quirm.net.
